overview: Britt is turning 30, and she's hitting a wall . . . she's been in a six-year relationship with her partner Tracy, and working hard for that promotion at work, but something's missing - somewhere along the way Britt lost herself. So, when her semi-estranged, Canadian-famous, rock star of a father shows up to her 30th birthday dinner, and Tracy springs a proposal on her all in one night, Britt is forced to shift her perspective inwards and think about what she wants.
title: Medium Young
